22
00:01:20,100 --> 00:01:21,900
Is your brain broken?

23
00:01:22,030 --> 00:01:22,760
System.

24
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:24,660
Scan that pretty boy.

25
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,260
