26
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:28,460
Scanning target's realm... Peak Quasi-Emperor.

27
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:29,920
Quasi... Quasi-Emperor?

28
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:31,200
