50
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,030
Oh.

51
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,030
Odd changes, even doesn't.

52
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:26,130
Palace Jade Liquid Wine.

53
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:26,829
Senior, this...

54
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:28,730
